 [[Ramones]] for the first time with music manager [[Danny Fields]]\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal bar|Biography|Arts|Music|Film|LGBT}}\n* [[Loureedia]], a genus of (underground) velvet spiders named for Lou Reed\n{{clear}}\n\n==References==\n'''Notes'''\n{{reflist|group=nb}}\n\n'''Citations'''\n{{reflist|30em|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"MPC-object\">{{cite web\n  |title      = 270553 Loureed (2002 GG178)\n  |work       = Minor Planet Center\n  |url        = https://www.minorplanetcenter.net/db_search/show_object?object_id=270553\n  |accessdate = September 5, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MPC-Circulars-Archive\">{{cite web\n  |title      = MPC/MPO/MPS Archive\n  |work       = Minor Planet Center\n  |url        = https://www.minorplanetcenter.net/iau/ECS/MPCArchive/MPCArchive_TBL.html\n  |accessdate = September 5, 2019}}</ref>\n\n}} <!-- end of reflist -->\n\n'''Bibliography'''\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Beeber|first1=Steven Lee|title=The Heebie-Jeebies at CBGB's: A Secret History of Jewish Punk|url=https://books.google.com/?id=tDk6FuQcxpoC&pg=PA11&lpg=PA11&dq=Toby+Futterman+Sidney+Joseph+Reed|isbn=9781556527616|year=2006|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Bockris|first1=Victor|title=Transformer: The Lou Reed Story|year=1994|isbn=0-684-80366-6|authorlink=Victor Bockris|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/transformerlour000bock}}\n* {{cite book|last=Brown|first=Bill|title=Words and Guitar: A History of Lou Reed's Music|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6JIpBgAAQBAJ|year=2013|publisher=Colossal Books|isbn=9780615933771|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=DeCurtis|first=Anthony|title=Lou Reed: A Life|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VdIpDgAAQBAJ|year=2017|publisher=Hodder & Stoughton|isbn=9781444794595|authorlink=Anthony DeCurtis|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Clapton|first=Diana|url=https://books.google.com/?id=cHb_AgAAQBAJ&pg=PT21&lpg=PT21&dq=Lou%20Reed%20hepatitis%20from%20a%20negro%20named%20jaw#v=onepage|title=Lou Reed & The Velvet Underground|year=2012|publish